    npx:hasSignature "M5EUBsO0I2kMXF3ZLNvKV6NiYNe/O1U290durwPjOgUiEN05Hynq+hGIhpmLT1atgL7t7ISxcPFPJaf2xstNAAyw0YGTENwHg8FrpDHqfLCcZUiTwLF4Wi+FrSfIBCKZCnIRj+w8f0FtAwSLYe733Ul/H/H0wNgrTkMRZ91btGM=";
